{
  "stem": "4686.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the-- and the parents became worried that we children, growing children, don't get enough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after we had dinner and grandpa said his prayers, the kids were taken out to a little side room where we had special wooden plates and special little knives.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were given some szalonna, what is pork fat, smoked, what is to give you energy and grow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was strictly only eaten all there with-- because that was [? terrible. ?] But that was only for the three of us children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And was the fact that you did keep this up and-- and still had Shabbat, was that helpful to you and-- and provided some kind of strength for you?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so, because we tried to stick as much to the normal as it is-- as it was possible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we did it at home, because to go to the synagogue, there was-- I don't think there was even synagogue by then.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, inside our house-- look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it was air raid time, so the windows was very blackened anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and you can't look-- you couldn't look into our-- our house, because even in normal times, wooden covers were on our-- particularly on our windows, to close off the outside at the evening.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the house was closed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a closed house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And only we were in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Look.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't much change.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was even more restricted to go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was even more difficult to get food, but we still got food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and the only thing started that they started to take the women into work battalions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they did it in the easiest way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to report in this and that sports ground.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
